description: '''Natanael Rub√©n Cano Monge''' (born 27 March 2001) is a Mexican rapper, musician and singer. Natanael is known for his fusion of [[trap music]] and [[regional Mexican]] [[corridos]], known as ''[[corridos tumbados]]''. The idea to fuse the two genres was proposed by Dan Sanchez who wrote Natanael's first corrido tumbado, "Soy el Diablo".
